title: NBA head coach: Sefolosha's character 'of the highest order'
text: NBA head coach: Sefolosha's character 'of the highest order' Thursday, 8 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) An NBA head coach has testified that the character of a professional basketball player on trial after a confrontation with New York City police is "of the highest order."
